user story: 
  group gets food
  gets bill
  one person pays
  {terry end}

  google oauth/local login
  
  person pulls out app
  adds friends at table with qr code
  person uploads receipt and adds tip
  creates group with added friends
  sends link to everyone by email
    (screencast dual screen)
  
  everyone logs in, opens shared socket table
  socket editing:
    uploader controls lockable columns and can notify users by email
    everyone can live remove rows, edit, and add users
    features: costs
  saves to database during live edit

  back to home screen, can see total spendings for user and also debts 

  also can click groups and see each groups receipts

